    "Predictive Healthcare Analytics.",
    "IoT systems can analyze historical patient data and current context [66] to predict health risks and trends, thereby better anticipating health complications.",
    "Telemedicine.",
    "Context-awareness enhances telemedicine by providing additional contextual information to remote healthcare providers.",
    "Realtime context, such as patient location [67] and vital signs, enhances the accuracy of telemedicine consultations and enables better-informed decisions."
